metadata.name: Not A Hand
metadata.description:
This piece along with "Octovision" were very out of the normal for me. It was a step in a brand new direction that I was not at all familiar with. At the time I had people ask me what the piece meant, and to this day I'm still not sure. I do know that I tapped into something while creating it though. 

This original piece is 7.5" x 6" and is redeemable only by the collector of the NFT. Please reach out via twitter to discuss further details after the purchase has been fulfilled.
